data.description: Large single level home on 1.23 acres walking distance to Eagle High School with infill Development Potential! Existing home has an exceptional floor plan for a large family with multigenerational and/or mother-in-law setup with two primary bedrooms with en-suite bathrooms, bonus room, two fireplaces, and covered back patio. Property zoned Mixed Use allowing for office, commercial, or high density residential, up to 20-units per acre. New sewer line is already located in Flint Dr. Home could also be used for assisted living, daycare, office, or single family home with space for your business. This is a great opportunity to own and develop in Eagle. Property has RV parking, irrigation water, two storage units, 220V power to back shed, and is surrounded by new development. Buyer to verify development details with the city, BTVA.
